# Component Rules

For component creation: `.ai/skills/create-component.md`

## Pattern summary

- Use `cva` for variants, `cn()` for class merging
- Add `data-slot` attribute for identification
- Props extend `React.ComponentProps<"element">`
- Named exports only (no default exports)
- File naming: `kebab-case.tsx`

